                                            <span style="background-image: url(https://img5tv.cdnvideo.ru/webp/shared/files/201807/2597_788944.jpg)" class="image">
                                                <span class="labl _onImg fsMedium">03:10</span>
                                            </span>
                                        <p class="fsBig link"><strong>«След. Кто кого»</strong></p>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                                                    <div class="col3">
                                                                    <a href="https://www.5-tv.ru/projects/film/1506283/" class="linkBlock">
                                            <span style="background-image: url(https://img5tv.cdnvideo.ru/webp/shared/files/201206/2597_219124.jpg)" class="image">
                                                <span class="labl _onImg fsMedium">03:40</span>
                                            </span>
                                        <p class="fsBig link"><strong>«След. Пикник»</strong></p>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                                                    <div class="col3">
                                                                    <a href="https://www.5-tv.ru/projects/film/1506468/" class="linkBlock">
                                            <span style="background-image: url(https://img5tv.cdnvideo.ru/webp/shared/files/201902/2597_887853.jpg)" class="image">
                                                <span class="labl _onImg fsMedium">04:10</span>
                                            </span>
                                        <p class="fsBig link"><strong>«След. Пираты»</strong></p>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                                                    <div class="col3">
                                                                    <a href="https://www.5-tv.ru/projects/film/1512399/" class="linkBlock">
                                            <span style="background-image: url(https://img5tv.cdnvideo.ru/webp/shared/files/202008/2976_1161107.jpg)" class="image">
                                                <span class="labl _onImg fsMedium">04:45</span>
                                            </span>
                                        <p class="fsBig link"><strong>«Свои-2. Нечего терять»</strong></p>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
